{
  "chapter": 107,
  "chapter_summary": "飞马牧场面临四大寇联军压境，气氛紧张。寇仲和徐子陵在膳园与兰姑周旋后，借口为李秀宁送糕饼前往环绿园。发现李秀宁正在接客后，二人怀疑牧场内奸作祟，决定分头行动。寇仲换上夜行衣潜入环绿园，偷听到内奸苑儿向李秀宁散布商秀洵与李密勾结的虚假情报，企图离间飞马牧场与李阀的关系。徐子陵则翻出城外侦察敌情，发现四大寇联军正向牧场推进。寇仲潜入李秀宁闺房时，被李秀宁的情人柴绍当场发现。本章揭示了李密通过内奸苑儿操纵飞马牧场局势的阴谋，同时展现了寇仲和徐子陵的夜行潜入能力和各自的性格特点。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "场主严令内堡的人，除非获有指派任务，否则须留在所属院落，违者按家法惩处，你们清楚了吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "无论是否打仗，大家仍要吃饭，所以兰姑你向我们颁此严令，是否多此一举呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "膳园是谁在管事，我要你们留在这里你们就一步都不准踏出门口，否则莫怪我不客气。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_lan_gu",
      "text": "兰姑息怒，刚才大管家向场主报告四大寇联军的先头部队在附近出现时，我们刚好跟场主谈及我们住房方面待遇上的问题。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小晶的记性此较好，当时场主怎么说呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当时场主着我们尽可安心。还得多弄点糕饼招待宁公主和她的随从，绝不要慌慌张张，有失我们牧场谈笑用兵的泱泱大度。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "兰姑",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "既是场主吩咐，你们还留在这里干甚么？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning_de_cong_wei",
      "speaker_name": "从卫",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "是否有甚么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning_de_cong_wei_b",
      "speaker_name": "另一从卫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "交给我们就成啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning_de_cong_wei",
      "text": "今早秀宁公主来参观膳园时，曾吩咐小人们弄好糕饼后须向她解说制法，请两位大爷通传一声。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "守卫",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "公主正接待客人，又不是甚么要紧的事，我们先报上去，稍后是否要见你们再由公主定夺，你们把东西交给我们好了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "李秀宁在接待哪一个呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "当然是牧场的人，对她来说就是客人。噢！不好！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们立即分头行事，记得回去取你的井中月。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "外面随时打上个十天半月，这里才是形势危急。你怎能这么快的就溜了去玩儿，却留下我孤零零一个人在这里捱苦。",
      "tone": "抱怨",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若我们一起出动，太易惹人疑心，别忘了体型高度是变不了的。而且我们要练习独当一面，好为将来作准备，明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今晚就让我们扬州双怪分头出动，闹他娘的一个天翻地覆。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若有人发觉我们不在这里，追问起来，我们就说是到了鲁先生处学艺，清楚了吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那不若回来时先到鲁妙子处集合，就更万无一失了。来吧！没有义气的家伙！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我怎样没义气了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "还说有义气？好玩的就自己去玩，剩下我一个人在这里吃西北风，呆等敌人发动阴谋。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁叫你那么多情呢？英雄救美，自是非你莫属。记着天明前我们在鲁先生处集合。好自为之吧！请恕小弟失陪了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_er",
      "speaker_name": "苑儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "宁公主现在该明白了吧。场主自认识了李天凡，且往来日密，所以很可能会向李密提供战马和装备。大管家和部分执事虽大力反对，却是屡劝无效。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "李纲",
      "listener": "char_yuan_er",
      "text": "此事非同小可，不知夫人此来，尊夫是否知道呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_er",
      "speaker_name": "苑儿",
      "listener": "char_li_gang",
      "text": "这个当然，是老爷嘱苑儿趁此良机，到来与诸位报讯和商量，希望我们和贵阀的关系，不致因场主一时胡涂而遭破坏。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "窦威",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "这确是奇怪，因为据我们所知，李密实是暗中支持四大寇扰乱南方的祸首，为何四大寇又会来攻打牧场呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_er",
      "speaker_name": "苑儿",
      "listener": "char_dou_wei",
      "text": "此事老爷亦曾作分析，可能是一个故弄玄虚，所以才千叮万嘱苑儿必须趁早通知各位，因为这极可能是场主受李天凡煽动下做的一次胡涂行为。",
      "tone": "从容",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "窦威",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "宁公主，不管怎样，我们亦须立即加强防御才成。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_dou_wei",
      "text": "来者不善，善者不来。若此事确有洵姐参与，对我们的实力定是了如指掌，则想防也防不了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_yuan_er",
      "text": "苑姐可否代为通知大总管，彼此作一次秘密详谈呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_er",
      "speaker_name": "苑儿",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "现在苑儿立即遣人通知老爷，他负责守卫东峡，除非是军情紧急，否则该没有问题的。",
      "tone": "从容",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "窦威",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "公主认为那苑儿的话是否可信呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "speaker_name": "李秀宁",
      "listener": "char_dou_wei",
      "text": "商秀洵岂是这种卑鄙小人，但防人之心不可无，一切待见过商震再说吧。唔！有没有办法可查到苑儿的出身来历呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_gang",
      "speaker_name": "李纲",
      "listener": "char_li_xiu_ning",
      "text": "一时可没有办法…",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chai_shao",
      "speaker_name": "柴绍",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "朋友夜闯环绿园，请问有何贵干呢？",
      "tone": "冷静",
      "chapter": 107,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    }
  ],
